# Zotero MCP Lite Configuration
# Full Local Mode - No Configuration Required

# ============================================================
# Requirements
# ============================================================
# 1. Zotero Desktop must be running
# 2. Enable local API in Zotero:
#    Settings -> Advanced -> General
#    Check "Allow other applications to communicate with Zotero"
# 3. Verify: http://127.0.0.1:23119/connector/ping

# ============================================================
# Optional: Custom Paths
# ============================================================
# Only needed if Zotero data is in non-standard location

# ZOTERO_DATABASE_PATH=/path/to/zotero.sqlite
# ZOTERO_DATA_DIR=/path/to/Zotero

# ============================================================
# Optional: Library Configuration
# ============================================================
# Only needed for non-default library

# ZOTERO_LIBRARY_ID=0
# ZOTERO_LIBRARY_TYPE=user
